Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:08.15,Narration,,0,0,0,,This story took place shortly after \NKokkuri-san started to haunt Kohina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:13.85,Default-I,,0,0,0,,She hasn't asked me to leave lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:17.03,Default-I,,0,0,0,,I think she's become attached to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kokkuri-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to stick around?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you be lonely without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:46.38,Narration,,0,0,0,,After that, Kokkuri-san was in a world of his own for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really... So I was the only one who thought we were friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Without hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this one-sidedness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bothersome... Not really... I don't care... Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:06.52,Narration,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri-san is an adult who's easily hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My cooking is worse than those 3 minute meals?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really... Not really... Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just an unneeded fox...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.99,0:01:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't matter at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really... Not really... Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:36.01,Default-I,,0,0,0,,My words seem to have hurt Kokkuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:42.51,Default-I,,0,0,0,,Even as a doll, I know what to say in cases like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really... Whatever... Not Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You even said it twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated it because it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person ever to annoy a doll to this extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-san is about to stop breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Having feelings means defeat for a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't like a ten-year-old made of glass, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A ten-year-old...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As an apology...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.89,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cup noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cup noodles! Cup noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kohina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohina-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:11.17,Narration,,0,0,0,,And so, Kokkuri-san got a cursed bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:16.88,Narration,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Frankly, he wished none of this had happened, and just wanted to go home.
